<h1>What we do</h1>

<p>
SmartFlix is a service that rents DVDs - just like your
corner video store - but we rent the kind of videos that you can't
find on every street corner.  Videos on running lathes, making glass
beads, welding steel, oil painting, building guitars... cool videos!
</p>

<p>
SmartFlix began serving hobbyists and hardware hackers in early 2003, and
has been growing explosively since then.
</p>


