<h2>Fun Facts</h2>

<p>
The first video we rented out was "Fundamentals of Machine Lathe Operation"...on VHS.
</p>

<p>
In our first month of operation, we rented out one video.  In the
second month, we rented three videos.  In our third month, we rented
out 14 videos...and growth has remained steady since then!
</p>

<p>
SmartFlix is - to the best of our knowledge - the largest
how-to video rental store in the world.
</p>

<p>
SmartFlix runs entirely on open source software: we use
Apache, Linux, PERL, mySQL, emacs, the Gimp, ruby, and KDE to get our
jobs done.
</p>

<p>
Dogs are welcome in the SmartFlix offices.  Given that most employees have at
least one dog, there have been occasions when there have been more
dogs than people here!
</p>

